**The branded leather pouch is a sleek and stylish accessory crafted from high-quality calf skin leather in a classic black color. The leather is soft and supple, providing a luxurious feel that is both durable and long-lasting. The pouch features a single front pocket with a magnetic closure, providing easy access to your essentials. The interior of the pouch is designed with six card slots, which are perfect for organizing credit cards, ID cards, or business cards, as well as one open pocket for additional storage. The card slots are lined with calf leather, which adds a layer of protection and durability. The pouch has a zip closure with a detachable wristlet, which allows for easy carrying and keeps your belongings safe and secure. The wristlet has an 18 cm (7.1") drop and can be adjusted to fit your wrist comfortably. The overall dimensions of the pouch are 18 cm (7.1") in height, 25 cm (9.8") in width, and 6 cm (2.3") in depth, providing ample storage space for all your essentials. The hardware of the pouch is finished in silver, adding a touch of elegance and sophistication. Additionally, the pouch features the monogram style stitching of the letters "GT" on the front, adding a personalized touch to the accessory. The stitching is done in a subtle and tasteful way, providing a stylish and distinctive look to the pouch. Overall, the branded leather pouch with "GT" stitching is a versatile and functional accessory that combines style and practicality. It's perfect for everyday use or for special occasions, and the monogram style stitching adds a unique and personalized touch to the accessory.** - Upscaled by <@1077842119462494218> (fast)
